	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Novum hunc annum, compater in domino charissime, tibi ac tuis omnibus opto per omnia faustum et omnis calamitatis expertem simulque pro strena <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2207" cert="high">Ioanni Heinrychulo</persName>, meo filio, tuo in Christo, missa gratias ago quam possum maximas.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Oro dominum, ut, quod facis, in multos annos feliciter facias et locum in te habeat illud Christi: Beatius est dare quam accipere.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Caeterum septima huius literas ex <placeName ref="l1976" cert="high">Augusta</placeName> mea accepi missas a d. <persName type="auto_name">Mekardo</persName>, in quibus sunt quae tibi significanda esse existimavi.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nempe ista: <placeName type="auto_name">Concordiam</placeName> in causa eucharistiae inter vos et d. <persName ref="p540" cert="high">Calvinum</persName> institutam quidam admodum commendant, et iudicant esse medium quoddam, quo partes contendentium conciliari queant.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Et ad hanc doctus ille ac pius baro <persName ref="p8041" cert="high">Iohannes a Lasco</persName>, qui nunc misera <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830">Anglia</placeName> relicta in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l825">Dania</placeName> agit, suo scripto illustrissimum electorem <persName ref="p17927" cert="high">Palatinum</persName> et caeteras quoque quas potest ecclesias hortatur, ut in illa tandem evangelici omnes contra Antichristum conveniant.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec ille.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Qua de re si quid et ipse accepisti, obsecro communica.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Adiecit de marchione ad hunc modum: "Interposuerunt se dux <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l572">Wirtemp[ergicus]</placeName> et <placeName ref="l619" cert="high">Bavarus</placeName> una cum duobus marchionibus electore et Ioanne pro ineunda concordia inter marchionem et ligam Noricam.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Res serio agitur; marchio petit ingentem summam auri; dux <placeName ref="l1041" cert="high">Brunsvicensis</placeName> rediit in ducatum suum."</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec ille.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quomodocunque habeat causa marchionis, certe scio secretarium illius intimum mihi notissimum praeterita septimana transisse per nos in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464">Galliam</placeName> ad regem.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Denique in episcopatu <placeName ref="l61" cert="high">Bremensi</placeName> colliguntur iam 6000 equitum.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sunt, qui suspicantur conscribi illos a Caesare, ut vi magna filium suum per <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2498">Germaniam</placeName> traducat in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830">Angliam</placeName> illisque postea contra <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464">Gallum</placeName> utatur.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gallus non satis fuit vigilans, quod <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830">Angliam</placeName> attinet.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hae nuptiae magnum illi malum, nisi occurrat in tempore, minari videntur.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Interea spero dominum non deserturum causam fidelium suorum, imo magis suam ipsius.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Optime vale, compater charissime.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Min <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20374">Margret</persName> und kinder wünschent euch allen vil guts und ein gantz glückhaftigs jar.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutem quaeso omnibus isthic fratribus et amicis, d. <persName ref="p8127" cert="high">Pellicano</persName>, d. <persName ref="p8171" cert="high">Bibliandro</persName>, d. <persName ref="p8011" cert="high">Gvalthero</persName>, m. <persName type="auto_name">Zwinglio</persName> et reliquis omnibus.</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernę</placeName> 1554. 10. ianuarii.</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8417" cert="high">W[olfgangus] Musc[ulus]</persName>, tuus compater in domino.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praestantissimo theologo m. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, compatri suo in domino charissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tiguri.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
